HEADWORD: Prosiphon
<hw>Pro*si"phon</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>pro-</ets> for + <ets>siphon</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
